data.description: Wonderful opportunity to live near Rio Pinar Golf Course and in the Heart of Orlando! Walking distance to grocery and restaurants and just 15 minutes from Downtown Orlando. You'll love all of the natural light that pours into the living room as you step inside along with the laminate floors throughout the living and bedrooms. This 1/2 duplex features 2 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom and a spacious backyard and covered porch.  In the kitchen, you'll love how much room there is plus access to your indoor laundry room. All the major systems have been taken care of for you so all you need to do is move right in and make this house your home! Brand New Roof January 2023 and New A/C Nov 2023.
